    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reform council tax so it is based on square footage and not value",
        "additional_details": "We want the Government to overhaul the council tax system, so this is based on the square footage of the property. We think this would make the tax burden fairer.",
        "background": "We want council tax bands to be based on square footage of the building, and not the value of the property. We believe current council tax bands aren't fair.\r\n \r\n",
